The Kismet control panel allows users to filter Wi-Fi devices based upon MAC address, advertised SSID or
beacon vendor tag. 
The best way to detect drones is by filtering individualized 802.11 vendor tags. IEEE keeps an open-source record of all registered company 802.11 vendor tags. Some notable ones are listed below: 

**DJI** 

• 60-60-1F
• 34-D2-62
• 48-1C-B9 

**Parrot** 

• 00-12-1C
• 90-03-B7
• A0-14-3D
• 00-26-7E 

